LIVE THE DREAM
/.header-wrap
Lakeside Oaks Mobile Home Park is a 55 and older mobile home park for active adults.  Our location is just on the outskirts Dade City Florida.  We are convenient to shopping, dining, and medical services, but surrounded by orange groves, trees and Lake Pasadena.  We are also convenient to Tampa and Orlando area attractions and the beach.   Our park offers low cost lot rent and nice homes available for sale .   We have singlewides and doublewides to choose from.  Ask about financing.
Whether you are looking for a permanent home, retirement vacation home, or a snowbird winter escape, come take a look at our available homes for sale.
